&quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":701,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/15\/they-innovated-after-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":19199,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Bidah: You do not know what they innovated after you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Some of my companions will come towards me at the Fountain in the Hereafter until I recognize them. They will be taken away from me, then I will say: My companions! It will be said: You do\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":992,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/08\/13\/sometimes-fasted-or-iftar\/","url_meta":{"origin":19199,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Companions fasted and broke fast during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: We would travel with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and those who fasted did not blame those who broke their fast, and those who broke their fast did not blame those who fasted. In another narration, Abu Sa'id al-Khudri said: Their view is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5345,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/19\/allah-only-merciful\/","url_meta":{"origin":19199,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: Allah is only merciful to the merciful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily,\u00a0Allah is merciful only to His servants who are merciful.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7448, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 923 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19199,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\